It is not the action of dancing, singing or playing itself, but the personality of the artist, his character, that captivates the public with his art.
The search for an encounter with the essential, with the elf that becomes visible in a way of feeling, of being and of being are and have been the constant of this work that is presented these days in the gallery El Fotomata.
