U.S. Treasury Secretary Henry Paulson, House Speaker Nancy Pelosi and the Republican representative at the negotiating table, Sen. Judd Gregg, announced the good news a few minutes after midnight yesterday, at the end of a marathon of negotiations that lasted two days.
