Democratic Senator Barack Obama was granted certain provisions to reach the agreement, particularly that it would allow owners to keep their domicile and that on the salary of the leaders of the companies survived by the state.
" When taxpayers are asked to take extraordinary measures because of the irresponsibility of some, there is no need to congratulate themselves.
